[thinking] **Evaluating class loader behavior**
[thinking] 
[thinking] I’m considering what happens when the native image Class.getClassLoader returns null for app classes. In that case, maybe I should look into using getSystemResource. I wonder if the report also covers getSystemResource, since the tests didn’t run any checks for that. I’m thinking about whether, under a native image, the app classes might have a specific class loader, like an image class loader. There’s a lot to unpack here!
